"40:84:5" : {s: 40, a: 84, w: 5, r: "امن", t: "ءَامَنَّا", l: "ءَامَنَ", lc: 537, tl: "āmannā", lb: "বিশ্বাস করা",e: "We believe", b: "আমরা ঈমান এনেছি", i: "kami beriman", f: 31, rm: "become/feel safe/secure, state of security/safety, trust, become quiet/tranquil in heart/mind, become free of expectation of evil or free of an object of dislike/hatred, promise/assurance of security/safety, become trustful/faithful/confident, to believe/acknowledge it, manifestation of humility/submission."},
